title: Eurovision Song Contest Helsinki 2007 DVD HD.TV.English.Commenta
description:
An alternative to Regenzy&#039;s Spanish PDTV recording of the Eurovision 2007 final.


Advantages:

*Much better quality (recorded HDTV BBC broadcast, but has MPEG encoding I think)

*Includes voting

*Narration in English and less disruptive than the Spanish version


Disadvantages:

*4 times bigger file size (so for the ones who don&#039;t need the vid urgently)

*In DVD format of 4 parts (you&#039;ll probably need something like Cyberlink PowerDVD   or similar to play it, &#039;cause it&#039;s worse quality if played with Windows Media Player)

Total duration: 32:12:29
    Video size: 720 x 576


V. good recording    ;)
